      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's crazy, i didn't even see the part about the thrust increase. that makes so much sense if they were reacting to something unexpected on the surface. about that \"major anomaly\" message... do you have any more info on that? specifically, is there any mention of where or what it was? i need to know if it connects back to the structures i've been reading about.",
